<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.8">
<l>putamiku vicumpil puṇariceṉ ṟaṇavap porukaṭa laravaṇait tuyiṉṟu</l>
<l>patamiku pariyiṉ mikuciṉan tavirtta paṉimukil vaṇṇartam kōyil</l>
<l>katamiku ciṉatta kaṭataṭak kaḷiṟṟiṉ kavuḷvaḻik kaḷivaṇṭu paruka</l>
<l>matamiku cāral māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart, we will worship in Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">with slopes where musth increases</l>
<l>From the cheeks of huge, rutting, raging elephants,</l>
<l rend="indent">their fury increasing, while bees sip [it], reeling,</l>
<l>The temple of the misty cloud-colored one who dispelled</l>
<l rend="indent">the increasing anger of the horse of increasing stride,</l>
<l>Having slept on a serpent bed in the crashing sea, as waves rose,</l>
<l rend="indent">reaching into the sky with increasing clouds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
